com.vmware.vapi.bindings

Interface DynamicStructClassResolver


  • public interface DynamicStructClassResolver
    Resolver that specifies the target class for "dynamic data" conversion. That is the alternative of DynamicStructure when converting StructValue for dynamic field to bindings type.

    • Method Summary

      Methods

      Class<? extends StaticStructure> resolveTargetClass(StructValue strValue)

        the target type for the conversion or null if the type cannot be resolved
